{"tid":1654713,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"人權法集會13至20萬人參與 證港人無畏緊急法不割蓆","createTime":"2019-10-14T17:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T17:30:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3ae3fb224bcfda28861c999341a63f28db773277","tid":1654713,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"新聞稿<br />\n<br />\n人權法集會13至20萬人參與<br />\n證港人無畏緊急法不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集氣大會籌委會宣佈，經連夜利用航拍圖片進一步點算後，估計昨晚集會正式人數約為13至20萬人。<br />\n<br />\n今次是蒙面法實施以來首次合法集會，近20萬市民堅定上街，足證「不割蓆」、「和勇不分」不是口號，市民無畏惡法，堅定爭取五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n籌委會同時譴責警方採用不必要武力，阻礙參與和平集會的市民回家。此等惡行必會曝露於國際鎂光燈下。<br />\n<br />\n香港人權民主法案集氣大會籌委會<br />\n2019年10月15日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/USA1014_Channel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUSA1014_Channel&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm90UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=edb6e8ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/USA1014_Channel</a>"},{"pid":"8e6554893756c8e63dfe13ff1ce3bff2e7123f05","tid":1654713,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:18:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a2395389f7266cf9c3b9bac8906f41a1d31e13","tid":1654713,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif